If I’m not mistaken they have some premium Nerf content on their instas too. Gonna keep these elite 2.0 blasters handy, always gotta be ready for what’s next with @nerf and this crew… #NerfAd #OnToNerfHouse3?

node.text: What can I say about Frank that hasn’t been said? My entire life I never needed to look around for a role model, mine was picking me from school to to go practice and then helping me to with my homework once we got home. I couldn’t tell him I was tired because he had already worked a 10 hour day. His example paved the way for the rest of my life. I’ll forever be indebted to my dad for giving me my work ethic, my mindset, and everything in between that has helped me succeed. Love you pops. Happy fathers day!

Excited to announce that I have accepted the #ThisTooShallPass challenge to support charities suffering from the COVID-19 pandemic. We all need to do our part in rebuilding struggling communities. 

I am calling out my friends @tombrady @jimmyfallon @adamweitsman to join me in supporting this cause by throwing a pass for charity.  Follow @kindboost and go to link in bio to learn more. #KindBoost
